                  comprehensive survey that investigates all the most common and
                  representative spatio-temporal trajectory measures. First, we
                  provide an overview of spatio-temporal trajectory measures in
                  terms of three hierarchical perspectives: Non-learning vs.
                  Learning, Free Space vs. Road Network, and Standalone vs.
                  Distributed. Next, we present an evaluation benchmark by
                  designing five real-world transformation scenarios. Based on
