                  metrics and postprocessing; then, we discuss the major changes
                  in network architecture and training tricks for each model.
                  Finally, we summarize the essential lessons from YOLO's
                  development and provide a perspective on its future,
                  highlighting potential research directions to enhance
                  real-time object detection systems.},
